The slope of CNV will vary with latenesses in blocks 1-4, 5-8 and 10-13, but there is no CNV-like activity for block 9; 
The size of P3b correlates with the lateness of global deviant, or predictions in blocks 5-8; 
The more salient the last-heard global deviant is, the later the next global deviant is expected (in blocks 5-8). Correspondingly, the slower the increase in CNV; 

